{"title":"新山歌","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":4,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"新山歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火炮一声震动天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年岩石把家搬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清泉像匹白棉布，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上挂到地平川。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（湖北郧县）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兴修水利好处多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿水笑着上山坡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山青稻香水磨响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日子越来越快活。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（湖北均县）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天一个凸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天把凸消，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后天再来看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劈山一道槽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（湖北均县）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水库筑得像城墙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水圳弯弯十里长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任它天旱不下雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员自己当龙王。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（江西吉安）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锣声和太阳比早，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽灯和月亮比明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人群和星星比多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心要征服山河。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（浙江义乌）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洼地大丰收，一年月月秋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一二月治鱼三四月藕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五六月打蒲又麦收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月里拔麻收菱角，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九十月里过大秋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十一月里正打苇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十二月鱼业又抬头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河北文安）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大别山涧漂渡船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数里碧绿波浪翻；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿河两岸土翻身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河滩涝地变良田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河南商城）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}